      "content": "i know about the crisis lines, but they don't change the reality. they just give me something to do for an hour so i can go back to the same life tomorrow. it's not even that i'm \"in crisis,\" it's just that the fundamental setup of my life feels wrong. like i'm a glitch in the system. what if there isn't a \"way through\" this? what if the only way to actually find peace is to just... stop?",
